Usage: report_metal_fill [-help] [-file <string>] [-fill_area] [-fill_length]
                         [-mesh]

-help                  # Prints out the command usage
-file <string>         # wirte the report to the file (string, optional)
-fill_area             # Report area information for  metal fill
                       # (bool, optional)
-fill_length           # Report length information for  metal fill
                       # (bool, optional)
-mesh                  # Report mesh information for  metal fill
                       # (bool, optional)